360
00:17:23,976 --> 00:17:24,896
Mom, dig in.

361
00:17:24,896 --> 00:17:26,216
What are you waiting for?

362
00:17:26,216 --> 00:17:26,936
Dig in.

363
00:17:29,295 --> 00:17:30,256
Take this.

364
00:17:31,936 --> 00:17:33,775
You never listen to me.

365
00:17:34,976 --> 00:17:36,456
I know I can't tell you what to do.

366
00:17:38,375 --> 00:17:40,416
Never live on handouts.

367
00:17:41,855 --> 00:17:43,095
Come home if things get tough.

368
00:17:43,535 --> 00:17:44,896
You're always welcome home.

369
00:18:16,496 --> 00:18:17,615
Just go to bed.

370
00:18:19,416 --> 00:18:21,335
I told you
not to wait for me for dinner.

371
00:18:28,456 --> 00:18:29,095
What's wrong?

372
00:18:30,936 --> 00:18:32,456
Did you forget what today is?

373
00:18:36,416 --> 00:18:37,375
What is it?

374
00:18:39,256 --> 00:18:40,736
My mom went back to Ningzhou.

375
00:18:41,016 --> 00:18:42,896
We were supposed to
have dinner with her.

376
