I called you so many times.

377
00:18:46,095 --> 00:18:47,256
Why didn't you answer?

378
00:18:53,855 --> 00:18:54,896
I honestly forgot.

379
00:19:01,176 --> 00:19:02,936
There was a crucial scene today.

380
00:19:02,936 --> 00:19:04,496
No phone calls allowed on set.

381
00:19:07,256 --> 00:19:08,176
How convenient.

382
00:19:09,176 --> 00:19:10,496
My mom came to Shenzhen,

383
00:19:10,496 --> 00:19:11,896
and you've been busy.

384
00:19:14,295 --> 00:19:15,775
We've been dating for over a year.

385
00:19:16,335 --> 00:19:17,535
What's your plan?

386
00:19:18,135 --> 00:19:19,696
I'm exhausted. Let's talk tomorrow.

387
00:19:20,055 --> 00:19:20,656
No.

388
00:19:21,256 --> 00:19:22,775
Nobody sleeps until we settle this.

389
00:19:25,055 --> 00:19:26,656
My mom never approved of us.

390
00:19:26,976 --> 00:19:28,936
What are you trying to say
by acting like this?

391
00:19:28,936 --> 00:19:29,976
Nothing.

392
00:19:35,496 --> 00:19:36,496
Let's break up then.

393
00:19:48,936 --> 00:19:49,496
Fine.

394
00:20:02,055 --> 00:20:02,896
I'm sorry.

395
00:20:03,456 --> 00:20:04,775
I shouldn't have lost my temper.

396
00:20:06,736 --> 00:20:08,456
Please don't leave me.

397
00:20:12,815 --> 00:20:13,855
I'm not leaving you.

398
00:20:17,335 --> 00:20:19,416
Then why are you packing?

399
00:20:22,375 --> 00:20:24,936
I'll be in Huizhou for three months
for a new job.

400
00:20:30,696 --> 00:20:32,176
Will you come back?

401
00:20:37,855 --> 00:20:39,896
I just want to focus on my career now.

402
00:20:42,656 --> 00:20:44,375
Marriage isn't in my plans.

403
00:20:45,936 --> 00:20:47,416
Do whatever you want.

404
00:20:48,456 --> 00:20:50,216
Just don't leave me.

405
00:21:05,760 --> 00:21:08,256
♪I go 145♪

406
00:21:08,256 --> 00:21:10,752
♪Rushing down the line♪

407
00:21:10,752 --> 00:21:12,704
♪Six strings screaming♪

408
00:21:13,371 --> 00:21:14,736
♪I feel good♪

409
00:21:14,736 --> 00:21:16,055
Why are you shouting?

410
00:21:17,256 --> 00:21:18,575
So loud.

411
00:21:19,055 --> 00:21:20,976
Why do I have to suffer this
to make money?

412
00:21:21,496 --> 00:21:23,016
Living is suffering.

413
00:21:24,539 --> 00:21:27,067
♪Keep driving♪

414
00:21:29,947 --> 00:21:32,216
♪Next blues child♪

415
00:21:32,216 --> 00:21:34,696
Rock and roll never dies.

416
00:21:34,736 --> 00:21:36,335
Rock and roll never dies.

417
00:21:39,176 --> 00:21:40,575
What's your name?

418
00:21:41,496 --> 00:21:42,535
I'm Yi...

419
00:21:42,896 --> 00:21:43,696
Easy.

420
00:21:44,615 --> 00:21:45,535
Innovative.

421
00:21:45,815 --> 00:21:46,696
Innovative, huh?

422
00:21:46,696 --> 00:21:47,375
Innovative.

423
00:21:47,375 --> 00:21:49,016
- Easy it is then.
- Easy.

424
00:21:49,416 --> 00:21:50,535
- Easy.
- Easy.

425
00:21:55,643 --> 00:21:59,515
♪I go 145♪

426
00:22:05,135 --> 00:22:06,295
Why is it soda?

427
00:22:07,335 --> 00:22:09,095
Take it or leave it.

428
00:22:10,135 --> 00:22:12,055
Hongbing, I'm already twenty.

429
00:22:19,375 --> 00:22:21,976
Give this 5000 yuan
to your sister tonight.

430
00:22:22,575 --> 00:22:25,335
The remaining 200 is your commission.

431
00:22:25,335 --> 00:22:26,496
Okay.

432
00:22:26,496 --> 00:22:27,656
Thank you, Hongbing.

433
00:22:28,135 --> 00:22:29,255
You'll always be my dearest

434
00:22:29,255 --> 00:22:30,256
