435
00:22:30,256 --> 00:22:30,775
Enough.

436
00:22:30,775 --> 00:22:32,055
Let go.

437
00:22:35,855 --> 00:22:37,016
What was that name again?

438
00:22:37,335 --> 00:22:38,095
Easy.

439
00:22:39,135 --> 00:22:39,696
Easy.

440
00:22:41,575 --> 00:22:42,615
Is it English or Chinese?

441
00:22:42,615 --> 00:22:43,656
What does it mean?

442
00:22:43,936 --> 00:22:45,216
It means simple.

443
00:22:45,335 --> 00:22:46,456
Life is too complicated.

444
00:22:46,775 --> 00:22:47,936
Let's return to simplicity.

445
00:22:48,615 --> 00:22:50,656
Why don't you
call yourself "Yi" as in "One"?

446
00:22:51,256 --> 00:22:52,736
So simple. Just call yourself "Yi".

447
00:22:55,176 --> 00:22:57,216
Living like you and my sister

448
00:22:57,216 --> 00:22:58,575
