464
00:23:32,256 --> 00:23:33,896
You'll understand when you grow up.

465
00:23:36,016 --> 00:23:37,135
I'd rather die.

466
00:23:37,736 --> 00:23:39,775
You, my sister,

467
00:23:39,775 --> 00:23:42,575
my dad, and my mom
are all walking corpses.

468
00:23:42,575 --> 00:23:43,256
You know why

469
00:23:43,256 --> 00:23:44,855
so many Shaanxi people love rock?

470
00:23:45,375 --> 00:23:46,135
Why?

471
00:23:47,095 --> 00:23:48,216
What's the essence of rock?

472
00:23:51,256 --> 00:23:52,736
If you can't fly, run.

473
00:23:53,216 --> 00:23:54,815
If you can't run, walk.

474
00:23:54,815 --> 00:23:56,496
If you can't walk, crawl.

475
00:23:58,775 --> 00:24:01,775
Crawling is still moving forward.

476
00:24:03,135 --> 00:24:05,416
When you don't feel sad
even when crawling,

477
