497
00:25:38,939 --> 00:25:42,011
♪I'm asking myself♪

498
00:25:42,683 --> 00:25:45,851
♪I can give up anything♪

499
00:25:46,107 --> 00:25:49,915
♪Yet today I can't bear to leave♪

500
00:25:50,459 --> 00:25:53,499
♪You're not beautiful♪

501
00:25:53,851 --> 00:25:56,016
♪But you're utterly adorable♪

502
00:25:56,016 --> 00:25:56,896
Marry me.

503
00:25:59,227 --> 00:26:00,891
♪Cinderella♪

504
00:26:01,979 --> 00:26:05,019
♪My Cinderella♪

505
00:26:13,403 --> 00:26:16,219
♪I keep breaking your heart♪

506
00:26:17,179 --> 00:26:20,059
♪I'm always so cruel♪

507
00:26:21,019 --> 00:26:24,059
♪I tell you not to take it seriously♪

508
00:26:24,539 --> 00:26:27,579
♪Because I dare not believe it♪

509
00:26:28,827 --> 00:26:31,867
♪You are so beautiful♪

510
00:26:32,347 --> 00:26:35,739
♪And you're utterly adorable♪

511
00:26:37,563 --> 00:26:39,515
♪Cinderella♪

512
00:26:40,411 --> 00:26:43,451
♪My Cinderella♪

