Go right in, okay?

521
00:27:19,295 --> 00:27:20,736
No need to queue up.

522
00:27:20,936 --> 00:27:22,016
Twenty per person.

523
00:27:22,656 --> 00:27:23,815
Go right in.

524
00:27:23,815 --> 00:27:25,375
Twenty per person. Go right in.

525
00:27:25,815 --> 00:27:26,656
Want to

526
00:27:26,656 --> 00:27:27,335
