568
00:28:50,976 --> 00:28:53,176
(Hu Sanyuan came to his senses.)

569
00:28:54,295 --> 00:28:56,656
(The "corpse fall"
and somersault he performed)

570
00:28:56,656 --> 00:28:57,535
(for years)

571
00:28:58,176 --> 00:29:01,016
(mean nothing next to
a foreigner's trigger squeeze)

572
00:29:01,496 --> 00:29:03,216
(and blazing shot.)

573
00:29:04,055 --> 00:29:06,135
(The times aren't interested
in a new costume.)

574
00:29:06,736 --> 00:29:10,575
(They've ripped the whole stage
from the ground.)

575
00:29:11,931 --> 00:29:18,875
(Double Afterglow)

576
00:29:20,575 --> 00:29:21,335
Sanyuan.

577
00:29:22,375 --> 00:29:22,976
Troupe Leader.

578
00:29:23,855 --> 00:29:24,775
Here for the movie?

579
00:29:25,575 --> 00:29:26,855
Yeah, I just watched it.

580
00:29:26,855 --> 00:29:28,055
I didn't see you.

581
00:29:29,135 --> 00:29:30,375
It was dark in there.

582
00:29:30,375 --> 00:29:32,335
My face is dark too.
How could you see me?

583
00:29:33,976 --> 00:29:34,696
Was it good?

584
00:29:35,696 --> 00:29:37,615
Yeah, it was really good.

585
00:29:38,976 --> 00:29:41,246
No wonder everyone's watching movies,

586
00:29:41,246 --> 00:29:42,375
and not opera now.

587
00:29:50,936 --> 00:29:52,095
It's scorching.

588
00:29:52,855 --> 00:29:53,896
Let's grab a beer.

589
00:29:54,855 --> 00:29:55,496
Okay.

590
00:29:56,335 --> 00:29:58,456
(After nine years of construction,)

591
00:29:58,456 --> 00:30:00,656
(the entire 119-kilometer-long channel)

592
00:30:00,656 --> 00:30:04,535
(of the Chang'an Heihe
Water Diversion Project)

593
00:30:04,535 --> 00:30:06,256
(has been completed.)

594
00:30:06,615 --> 00:30:08,416
(Heihe River and Shitou River...)

595
00:30:09,896 --> 00:30:12,375
They keep talking about

596
00:30:12,375 --> 00:30:13,855
getting the Heihe River water.

597
00:30:13,855 --> 00:30:14,936
Where's the water?

598
00:30:15,256 --> 00:30:16,496
It's been so many years.

599
00:30:16,736 --> 00:30:18,135
I haven't seen a drop of it.

600
00:30:18,575 --> 00:30:21,335
They say the eight rivers
flow around Chang'an.

601
00:30:21,335 --> 00:30:22,135
Right?

602
00:30:22,135 --> 00:30:23,295
Now it should be,

603
00:30:23,295 --> 00:30:27,575
"Across Guanzhong I've searched,
to where Chang'an's eight rivers end."

604
00:30:29,375 --> 00:30:31,055
Everything has its pattern.

605
00:30:31,055 --> 00:30:32,448
The same goes for Qinqiang opera.

606
00:30:32,615 --> 00:30:35,176
Everything has its ups and downs.

607
00:30:35,535 --> 00:30:37,016
Qinqiang opera may be declining.

608
00:30:37,295 --> 00:30:38,016
But someday,

609
00:30:39,055 --> 00:30:40,055
it will rise again.

610
00:30:40,456 --> 00:30:42,696
What I care about now

611
00:30:43,256 --> 00:30:44,976
is whether I can

612
00:30:44,976 --> 00:30:48,295
see the water of the Heihe River
in my lifetime.

613
00:30:49,051 --> 00:30:51,921
(No Stage)

614
00:30:57,295 --> 00:30:58,095
Is that enough?

615
00:30:58,295 --> 00:31:00,216
Keep the money for Liu Yi's surgery.

616
00:31:00,216 --> 00:31:01,936
I found a job at this bar.

617
00:31:02,095 --> 00:31:03,855
Just take it.

618
00:31:03,855 --> 00:31:05,335
You have another task tonight.

619
00:31:05,335 --> 00:31:06,295
No need.

620
00:31:06,775 --> 00:31:07,736
I have money.

621
00:31:09,696 --> 00:31:11,575
You think you're so capable now, huh?

622
00:31:15,176 --> 00:31:15,771
Here.

623
00:31:17,216 --> 00:31:19,335
Give it to your sister tonight.

624
00:31:21,216 --> 00:31:22,055
I won't go.

625
00:31:23,615 --> 00:31:25,295
You think you're tough, huh?

626
00:31:25,815 --> 00:31:27,016
Being tough, are you?

627
00:31:27,016 --> 00:31:28,456
You won't even listen to me, huh?

628
00:31:28,456 --> 00:31:29,016
Take it.

629
00:31:29,016 --> 00:31:30,335
Why don't you go yourself?

630
00:31:30,335 --> 00:31:31,976
You're clearly not over her.

631
00:31:32,335 --> 00:31:34,295
You're hoping for her gentleness,

632
00:31:34,295 --> 00:31:36,256
reluctant to see her staying silent.

633
00:31:36,896 --> 00:31:37,936
You're so full of it.

634
00:31:37,936 --> 00:31:38,936
Where did you learn it?

635
00:31:38,936 --> 00:31:40,216
From the lyrics.

636
00:31:40,216 --> 00:31:41,696
You can learn from the songs.

637
00:31:42,535 --> 00:31:43,335
Take it.

638
00:31:43,335 --> 00:31:44,936
You'll keep suffering like this.

639
00:31:45,456 --> 00:31:47,896
Either you break it off,
or go see her yourself.

640
00:31:57,135 --> 00:31:57,896
Come on.

641
00:31:58,456 --> 00:32:00,416
Daddy will put some lotion on you, okay?

642
00:32:02,016 --> 00:32:03,696
Is the water cold? Try it.

643
00:32:04,656 --> 00:32:05,976
Can you stand it?

644
00:32:06,416 --> 00:32:07,896
Is it cold?

645
00:32:07,896 --> 00:32:08,855
Is it cold?

646
00:32:08,855 --> 00:32:09,696
Liu Yi.

647
00:32:10,095 --> 00:32:11,216
You're amazing.

648
00:32:12,456 --> 00:32:14,176
You get more amazing by the day.

649
00:32:14,176 --> 00:32:17,615
Dada...

650
00:32:17,615 --> 00:32:18,560
You're saying "Dad"?

651
00:32:21,256 --> 00:32:21,936
Liu Yi.

652
00:32:22,696 --> 00:32:24,135
You just called me "Dad", huh?

653
00:32:24,976 --> 00:32:25,855
Say it again.

654
00:32:26,896 --> 00:32:28,095
Come on.

655
00:32:28,095 --> 00:32:29,775
Come on, Liu Yi.

656
00:32:29,775 --> 00:32:30,456
Qin'e.

657
00:32:30,575 --> 00:32:31,656
Liu Yi just said "Dad".

658
00:32:32,055 --> 00:32:32,896
Dada...

659
00:32:32,896 --> 00:32:33,496
Right?

660
00:32:33,496 --> 00:32:35,216
Dada...

661
00:32:35,216 --> 00:32:36,496
Come on.

662
00:32:36,496 --> 00:32:37,496
Say "Mom".

663
00:32:37,855 --> 00:32:39,656
Nobody in this family
is greater than Mom.

664
00:32:40,016 --> 00:32:40,575
Say "Mom".

665
00:32:40,575 --> 00:32:41,416
Don't pressure him.

666
00:32:42,216 --> 00:32:44,176
I'm happy no matter who he's calling.

667
00:32:44,176 --> 00:32:45,416
Sit down and eat.

668
00:32:45,416 --> 00:32:46,135
Come on.

669
00:32:46,696 --> 00:32:48,535
How come you have time to come today?

670
00:32:49,055 --> 00:32:50,295
Did you swap shifts?

671
00:32:51,176 --> 00:32:53,736
I just won
the "Outstanding Individual" title.

672
00:32:54,815 --> 00:32:55,375
Look.

673
00:32:56,176 --> 00:32:57,456
A bonus.

674
00:32:57,456 --> 00:32:58,575
Liu Yi, look.

675
00:32:59,016 --> 00:33:01,256
Mommy made you some yummy food.

676
00:33:01,696 --> 00:33:03,055
Here, have a bite.

677
00:33:05,976 --> 00:33:06,496
What's wrong?

678
00:33:08,575 --> 00:33:09,855
Something on your mind?

679
00:33:09,855 --> 00:33:11,656
Nothing. Let's eat.

680
00:33:12,055 --> 00:33:12,736
Tell me.

681
00:33:13,416 --> 00:33:14,535
I'll cheer you up.

682
00:33:19,375 --> 00:33:19,963
Come on.

683
00:33:20,535 --> 00:33:21,936
Let's eat.

684
00:33:21,936 --> 00:33:24,375
Try the shredded potatoes Mommy made.

685
00:33:25,563 --> 00:33:26,203
Here.

686
00:33:34,656 --> 00:33:37,775
The vinegar-fried shredded potatoes
are amazing.

687
00:33:39,055 --> 00:33:42,656
The shreds are cut like carvings,
each one distinct.

688
00:33:42,656 --> 00:33:44,295
Qin'e, you're amazing.

689
00:33:44,295 --> 00:33:46,295
You're getting more and more capable.

690
00:33:46,295 --> 00:33:47,456
Isn't that right, Liu Yi?

691
00:33:49,256 --> 00:33:50,535
How am I capable?

692
00:33:51,095 --> 00:33:52,815
I'm in my thirties.

693
00:33:53,535 --> 00:33:55,535
But I can't do anything
besides singing opera.

694
00:33:57,055 --> 00:33:59,095
Sometimes I feel I don't sing opera

695
00:33:59,095 --> 00:34:00,656
with the same energy as before.

696
00:34:02,375 --> 00:34:03,535
Don't say that.

697
00:34:04,656 --> 00:34:05,496
Look at you.

698
00:34:06,055 --> 00:34:08,575
You've taken one thing and perfected it.

699
00:34:08,575 --> 00:34:10,535
That's really amazing, you know?

700
00:34:11,376 --> 00:34:12,416
There's something

701
00:34:12,416 --> 00:34:14,095
you really have to learn from me.

702
00:34:14,816 --> 00:34:16,695
Learn to praise yourself, okay?

703
00:34:17,255 --> 00:34:18,695
What's that big mirror for?

704
00:34:18,695 --> 00:34:20,055
You should look in the mirror.

705
00:34:21,135 --> 00:34:23,215
"How did I get so pretty?

706
00:34:23,856 --> 00:34:26,055
How come my voice is so mellow?

707
00:34:26,615 --> 00:34:28,255
My slender waist.

708
00:34:28,255 --> 00:34:31,456
When I do the Woyu posture,
my head touches the ground."

709
00:34:34,376 --> 00:34:35,496
Right?

710
00:34:35,496 --> 00:34:37,735
Mommy makes the best shredded potatoes.

711
00:34:38,416 --> 00:34:39,896
So authentic.

712
00:34:40,456 --> 00:34:42,615
That's enough.
I'm not as thick-skinned as you.

713
00:34:42,615 --> 00:34:43,976
What's wrong with it?

714
00:34:43,976 --> 00:34:45,856
Being thick-skinned makes one happy.

715
00:34:46,456 --> 00:34:47,255
Right, Liu Yi?

716
00:34:47,896 --> 00:34:49,976
Doesn't Mommy
make the best shredded potatoes?

717
00:34:50,456 --> 00:34:51,175
Praise Mommy.

718
00:34:51,776 --> 00:34:53,496
Say "Mom".

719
00:34:56,296 --> 00:34:56,816
Okay.

720
00:34:58,135 --> 00:34:59,615
Besides the potato shreds,

721
00:34:59,615 --> 00:35:01,896
the stir-fried tomato and eggs
is also amazing.

722
00:35:09,416 --> 00:35:10,615
Alright then, I'm off.

723
00:35:10,936 --> 00:35:11,776
Take care.

724
00:35:14,376 --> 00:35:14,976
Oh, right.

725
00:35:17,896 --> 00:35:18,496
Qin'e.

726
00:35:21,735 --> 00:35:22,735
Rest if you're tired.

727
00:35:23,776 --> 00:35:24,856
Stay where you are

728
00:35:25,175 --> 00:35:26,135
if you're lost.

729
00:35:27,695 --> 00:35:28,695
Or turn around.

730
00:35:30,055 --> 00:35:32,496
I promise, if you turn around,

731
00:35:33,615 --> 00:35:34,856
I'll be right behind you.

732
00:35:36,936 --> 00:35:37,535
I'm off.

733
00:35:54,592 --> 00:35:56,832
(Qinqiang Opera, Bai She Zhuan)

734
00:35:57,408 --> 00:36:00,416
♪yet trust that vile monk♪

735
00:36:00,416 --> 00:36:09,416
♪I tend to you in every heat and chill♪

736
00:36:09,416 --> 00:36:18,776
♪I cook for you every single day♪

737
00:36:18,776 --> 00:36:28,936
♪I braved the sacred mountain,
risking death to bring you remedy♪

738
00:36:31,135 --> 00:36:39,255
♪I flooded Jinshan Mountain
to fight that vile monk for you♪

739
00:36:43,936 --> 00:36:44,535
Uncle.

740
00:36:46,095 --> 00:36:47,856
Are you still mad at me?

741
00:36:50,296 --> 00:36:53,856
Wedding and funeral opera performances
had strict rules back then.

742
00:36:54,496 --> 00:36:56,095
The drummer was the most important.

743
00:36:57,255 --> 00:37:00,615
Musicians had to arrive before breakfast

744
00:37:01,496 --> 00:37:05,215
and lay out the instruments
on the Eight Immortals Table.

745
00:37:05,735 --> 00:37:08,816
After setting off firecrackers,
the performance began.

746
00:37:09,175 --> 00:37:10,535
Once the opening drum sounded,

747
00:37:11,055 --> 00:37:13,255
the host had to hand out red envelopes

748
00:37:13,255 --> 00:37:15,336
as gifts for the musicians.

749
00:37:16,816 --> 00:37:19,535
Just as there was an opening drum,
there was also a closing drum.

750
00:37:20,175 --> 00:37:22,095
The hosts want
a proper beginning and end,

751
00:37:22,615 --> 00:37:23,695
hoping for

752
00:37:25,255 --> 00:37:27,695
smooth sailing
and calm handling of affairs,

753
00:37:28,376 --> 00:37:30,856
turning misfortune into blessings.

754
00:37:32,672 --> 00:37:33,600
I've said too much.

755
00:37:34,856 --> 00:37:36,135
These are old traditions.

756
00:37:37,055 --> 00:37:39,175
Young people are no longer interested

757
00:37:39,175 --> 00:37:39,896
in those customs.

758
00:37:45,936 --> 00:37:48,416
What are we really watching
when we watch Qinqiang opera?

759
00:37:49,695 --> 00:37:51,055
We're watching a struggle.

760
00:37:51,936 --> 00:37:53,255
Survival.

761
00:37:54,615 --> 00:37:56,175
Defiance.

762
00:38:01,535 --> 00:38:04,336
You did nothing wrong.
You're tougher than anyone.

763
00:38:05,735 --> 00:38:07,296
You fully understand Qinqiang opera.

764
00:38:10,735 --> 00:38:12,215
But I misspoke earlier.

765
00:38:13,496 --> 00:38:15,055
Qinqiang opera hasn't failed me.

766
00:38:15,976 --> 00:38:18,655
Rest assured, I won't disgrace it.

767
00:38:22,655 --> 00:38:24,936
Sink your roots deep.

768
00:38:24,936 --> 00:38:26,296
Hold on. Stay alive.

769
00:38:27,135 --> 00:38:28,896
Then you'll see the rain come.

770
00:38:28,896 --> 00:38:31,816
Then you'll see
the Heihe River water flowing in.

771
00:38:34,135 --> 00:38:34,715
Okay.

772
00:39:23,336 --> 00:39:24,175
The water came.

773
00:39:25,976 --> 00:39:27,055
The water came.

774
00:39:27,055 --> 00:39:28,856
The water came.

775
00:39:28,856 --> 00:39:30,055
Get the water.

776
00:39:30,055 --> 00:39:31,496
The water came.

777
00:39:31,496 --> 00:39:32,416
The water came.

778
00:39:33,416 --> 00:39:34,695
The water came.

779
00:39:34,695 --> 00:39:35,195
Hurry up.

780
00:39:36,575 --> 00:39:37,615
The water came.

781
00:39:37,615 --> 00:39:39,296
(Good news
from the key construction site.)

782
00:39:39,296 --> 00:39:41,336
(After the hard work
of countless builders,)

783
00:39:41,336 --> 00:39:43,296
(the main structure has been completed)

784
00:39:43,296 --> 00:39:44,544
(six months ahead of schedule.)

785
00:40:03,215 --> 00:40:05,215
Thirty thousand, not a cent less.

786
00:40:05,456 --> 00:40:06,296
Count it.

787
00:40:06,695 --> 00:40:07,456
No need.

788
00:40:07,896 --> 00:40:08,936
I trust you.

789
00:40:09,575 --> 00:40:10,735
Let's make it clear.

790
00:40:10,735 --> 00:40:12,735
You get six months interest-free.

791
00:40:12,735 --> 00:40:15,095
After that, we follow standard terms.

792
00:40:15,735 --> 00:40:16,976
Three percent monthly interest.

793
00:40:18,336 --> 00:40:18,936
Understood.

794
00:40:19,376 --> 00:40:20,496
Thanks, Hei.

795
00:40:21,095 --> 00:40:24,296
You borrow money from me
and ask me to buy you food?

796
00:40:27,016 --> 00:40:28,856
Regular quality only. No premium stuff.

797
00:40:33,095 --> 00:40:34,575
The tapes you ordered last time.

798
00:40:35,055 --> 00:40:35,695
Take a look.

799
00:40:35,904 --> 00:40:36,800
We've got everything.

800
00:40:36,800 --> 00:40:37,695
Fifteen yuan per tape.

801
00:40:37,695 --> 00:40:38,376
This one's huge.

802
00:40:39,095 --> 00:40:39,707
I like it.

803
00:40:39,936 --> 00:40:40,667
Yeah.

804
00:40:41,296 --> 00:40:42,016
What's it called?

805
00:40:42,016 --> 00:40:42,735
Pink...

806
00:40:42,896 --> 00:40:43,579
Uncle.

807
00:40:43,816 --> 00:40:44,655
Floyd or something.

808
00:40:44,655 --> 00:40:45,296
This is good.

809
00:40:45,296 --> 00:40:45,976
Queen, right?

810
00:40:45,976 --> 00:40:46,816
- Come here.
- Uncle.

811
00:40:47,215 --> 00:40:48,215
Why are you here?

812
00:40:49,336 --> 00:40:51,135
Don't you know whose turf this is?

813
00:40:51,456 --> 00:40:53,095
I knew you were here from day one.

814
00:40:53,615 --> 00:40:55,416
If I hadn't put in a word with Hei,

815
00:40:55,816 --> 00:40:57,215
you think you could do this here?

816
00:40:58,376 --> 00:41:00,416
Aren't you love rivals?
You're working together?

817
00:41:00,416 --> 00:41:01,496
You talk too much.

818
00:41:03,816 --> 00:41:05,175
Well, why are you here?

819
00:41:05,655 --> 00:41:07,135
The kid's surgery is coming up.

820
00:41:07,135 --> 00:41:08,575
Got any plans?

821
00:41:09,615 --> 00:41:10,296
Of course.

822
00:41:10,615 --> 00:41:11,735
But my plans don't count.

823
00:41:12,296 --> 00:41:13,776
What happened to that persistence?

824
00:41:14,135 --> 00:41:16,215
You can't get a wife
if you care about pride.

825
00:41:16,215 --> 00:41:17,496
Now you care about pride?

826
00:41:19,055 --> 00:41:21,016
Whether I care about pride,
life must go on.

827
00:41:21,215 --> 00:41:22,016
How?

828
00:41:23,135 --> 00:41:24,320
I haven't figured it out.

829
00:41:25,456 --> 00:41:28,016
I don't even know
if I like Qin'e on stage

830
00:41:28,016 --> 00:41:29,496
or off stage.

831
00:41:29,816 --> 00:41:31,695
She's who she is on and off stage.

832
00:41:32,456 --> 00:41:34,255
You two are so full of drama.

833
00:41:34,816 --> 00:41:35,856
I haven't figured it out.

834
00:41:36,336 --> 00:41:37,496
You can take your time.

835
00:41:37,496 --> 00:41:38,535
But do your job.

836
00:41:40,816 --> 00:41:41,575
What do you mean?

837
00:41:41,575 --> 00:41:42,175
Remarry her.

838
00:41:43,496 --> 00:41:44,575
Get the kid treated.

839
00:41:44,575 --> 00:41:45,575
Do what needs to be done.

840
00:41:49,695 --> 00:41:50,255
Uncle.

841
00:41:50,695 --> 00:41:51,416
Take it.

842
00:42:40,135 --> 00:42:40,816
Cut.

843
00:42:41,336 --> 00:42:41,936
Good.

844
00:42:42,135 --> 00:42:43,496
Cut. The director called cut.

845
00:42:43,496 --> 00:42:44,376
Scene 25, get ready.

846
00:42:44,496 --> 00:42:45,255
Move!

847
00:42:45,255 --> 00:42:46,655
Scene 105, shot 12, take 5.

